  <span id="freeText8935980594633398256" style="display:none">A book to return to time after time. It's a wonderful and thought provoking story (based on one of Tolstoy's short stories) and is beautifully illustrated. It was a favourite with my kids when they were younger and is still a favourite of mine.</span>
