          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780439537636" href="/book/show/47828.The_Three_Questions">review of another edition</a>

          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">parents reading with their children</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=2010">2010</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=kindness">kindness</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=pets">pets</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=russia">russia</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=religion-philosophy">religion-philosophy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1019021-dolly?shelf=ocean-seashore">ocean-seashore</a>, 
